Suppose the modulation vector changes the weights.

Exploration mode:

Novelty: 0.8
Similarity: 0.2
Evidence: 0.3

Validation mode:

Novelty: 0.1
Similarity: 0.8
Evidence: 1.0

The graph itself is unchanged.

The field changes.

The path changes.

